      • getSpawnNodes

        public static java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>[] getSpawnNodes(java.lang.String edgeFile)
        Use to get dead end in graph. Nodes with no incoming edges will be spawn nodes (agent creation) and nodes with no outcoming edges will be despawn nodes (agent destruction).
        Parameters:
        edgeFile -
        Returns:
        Array of id node list, where the first list contains spawn nodes and the second list contains despawn nodes
